280
00:34:05,119 --> 00:34:06,720
[SPEAKER_03] 8, 9, 2, 2.

281
00:34:06,880 --> 00:34:08,480
[SPEAKER_03] E ali, negdje moraš udariti u zid.

282
00:34:08,639 --> 00:34:08,719
[SPEAKER_03] Da.

283
00:34:10,159 --> 00:34:11,199
[SPEAKER_03] Stićete onaj.

284
00:34:12,000 --> 00:34:12,719
[SPEAKER_03] Jer što ćeš onda?

285
00:34:13,199 --> 00:34:15,599
[SPEAKER_03] pet, pa šest, pa sedam, pa osam, pa koliko?

286
00:34:16,639 --> 00:34:17,519
[SPEAKER_03] Se ne možeš.

287
00:34:18,000 --> 00:34:20,320
[SPEAKER_03] Jednostavno telo ti ne može to podnit.

288
00:34:20,800 --> 00:34:23,039
[SPEAKER_03] Ni glava, ni mozak, ni ništa.

289
00:34:23,280 --> 00:34:25,280
[SPEAKER_03] Jednostavno ideš unazad.

290
00:34:26,079 --> 00:34:28,800
[SPEAKER_03] A onaj drugi samo te stiže.

291
00:34:29,280 --> 00:34:30,000
[SPEAKER_03] I ona panika.

292
00:34:31,760 --> 00:34:33,440
[SPEAKER_02] Tako da vidiš kako me uvatio.

293
00:34:35,760 --> 00:34:37,599
[SPEAKER_03] Minja je trenera, ne valja trenera.

294
00:34:37,760 --> 00:34:39,840
[SPEAKER_03] Odmah, odmah, trenera, sve minja.

295
00:34:40,559 --> 00:34:43,119
[SPEAKER_03] Grad, trenera, klub, sve, ništa ne valja.

296
00:34:44,719 --> 00:34:46,559
[SPEAKER_02] Da, da, majko moja.

297
00:34:47,840 --> 00:34:48,800
