323
00:36:57,440 --> 00:37:03,760
[SPEAKER_03] Znači, ti ideš spavati dok dođeš u hotel, dok ono prije 7-8 ujutro.

324
00:37:04,400 --> 00:37:10,320
[SPEAKER_03] I šta spavaš do 5 popodne i ti moraš igrati sutra.

325
00:37:10,639 --> 00:37:11,519
[SPEAKER_03] Mislim, to.

326
00:37:14,079 --> 00:37:16,559
[SPEAKER_03] Sad su nešto počeli minijati, ali opet nije to.

327
00:37:18,719 --> 00:37:26,079
