340
00:38:31,280 --> 00:38:32,079
[SPEAKER_03] To nisam znao.

341
00:38:33,679 --> 00:38:34,320
[SPEAKER_02] Duže izmjene.

342
00:38:34,880 --> 00:38:42,239
